    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《华夏山河：序幕》仅作为完整版中部分游戏内容的玩法演示。本版游戏完全免费，让您有机会切身感受在长城修建的历史过程中形成的华夏民族的定居点的生活点滴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为其中的民众之一，在建造世界上最伟大的防御工事的进程中不断挑战自身的各种技能。做好日常挑战的心理准备了吗？以下你可以看到整个故事的情况阐述：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317910/extras/a12ca5493bc30c6968c213d87135a086.poster.avif?t=1750423136\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317910/extras/a12ca5493bc30c6968c213d87135a086.webm?t=1750423136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>提升村子的生活质量：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 打造必要的工具</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 建造对村子极为重要的建筑及基础设施</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 生产建造长城所需的物件</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317910/extras/feec2a085037e6816e1d10f38ffbaa62.poster.avif?t=1750423136\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317910/extras/feec2a085037e6816e1d10f38ffbaa62.webm?t=1750423136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>从头开始建起一座信号塔：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 对全部资源规划使用</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 阅览设计图</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 参与各部分建设工作</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317910/extras/34bed9d38c849da53ad96425ad41d089.poster.avif?t=1750423136